freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I started with a circular rash on my upper shoulder.  I had not reported it before but wondering now if it is related.  It started about a week or two after my first injection.
On 3/1/21, I had a fever, chills, fatigue and headache.  It lasted 24 hours.  I was COVID tested on 3/2/21 and those results were negative.
